{"id":318815,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-人权捍卫者刘沙沙10月14日遭行政拘留5天今日/","date":"2013-10-19T15:33:50Z","modified":"2013-10-19T15:33:50Z","title":"维权网 | 人权捍卫者刘沙沙10月14日遭行政拘留5天今日出狱（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></span></p>\n<div><span></span> </div>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张兵报道）大陆著名人权捍卫者刘沙沙女士长期从事维权活动，经常受到当局的打压迫害。近日，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2013</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>14</span></span><span>日，河南省南阳油田公安局直属分局又以刘沙沙于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2013</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>7</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>1</span></span><span>日在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>twitter</span></span><span>网上，所发关于当时新疆和田事件的帖子为由，将其行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>5</span></span><span>天。刘沙沙在推特上的帖子是这样写的：“警方于周五</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>28</span></span><span>日向数百正在抗议的维吾尔人开枪，造成多大</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>15</span></span><span>人死亡，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>50</span></span><span>多人受伤。”</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>刘沙沙于今天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2013</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>19</span></span><span>日星期六）出狱。刘沙沙对此指控十分气愤，她表示：“内容里的伤亡数据是和田当局也证实了的。”</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>目前，中共当局妄图以打击谣言的方式，封杀民间舆论对它的抨击和维权运动的发展，而以传播谣言为罪名，对人权捍卫者刘沙沙的行政拘留，是当局继续以各种借口肆意镇压维权运动的有一例证。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-BATV4Q3R1DQ/UmJbNfnxvMI/AAAAAAAApsU/8kmPALX_SE4/s1600/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20131019180724.png\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-BATV4Q3R1DQ/UmJbNfnxvMI/AAAAAAAApsU/8kmPALX_SE4/s400/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20131019180724.png\" width=\"276\" /></a></div>\n<p> </p></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form meth